    public class SwaggerGuiceJaxrsScanner
extends com.wordnik.swagger.jaxrs.config.DefaultJaxrsScanner
    Finds JAX-RS resource classes via Guice, so that they can be scanned for Swagger API annotations.

    Like RESTEasy, this simply searches the injector for bindings that have a Path annotation.
